<h3 id="cp-3-contingency-training-l-m-h">CP-3 Contingency Training (L) (M) (H)</h3>
<p>The organization provides contingency training to information system users consistent with assigned roles and responsibilities:</p>
<ol type="a">
<li>Within [FedRAMP Assignment: ten (10) days] of assuming a contingency role or responsibility;</li>
<li>When required by information system changes; and</li>
<li>[FedRAMP Assignment: at least annually] thereafter.</li>
</ol>

